{"tid":599281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門中聯辦副主任陳斯喜指叫喊「結束一黨專政」的人不能參選立法會","createTime":"2018-03-20T09:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T13:49:26.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2a73e8513a69438f4638f237ef0d4cbbbbe8a247","tid":599281,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:15:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180320/mobile/bkn-20180320134500546-0320_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180320%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180320134500546-0320_00822_001.html&d=ZhIX5m104SAY8N8dsYFrA%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=8d3dc257\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180320/mobile/bkn-20180320134500546-0320_00822_001.html</a><br />\n新任全國人大常委譚耀宗昨日(19日)指，國家修憲後確立中國共產黨領導地位，高叫「結束一黨專政」口號人士牴觸憲法及《基本法》，或影響參選立法會資格。澳門中聯辦副主任陳斯喜今日(20日)亦指，據他理解，叫喊「結束一黨專政」的人，不能參選立法會。 <br />\n<br />\n陳斯喜解釋，國家憲法第一條規定，中國共產黨領導是中國特色社會主義最本質的特徵。被問及香港並非實行社會主義，陳斯喜指憲法是國家的根本法，香港雖是特別行政區，但要尊重憲法、維護憲法權威，這方面並沒有兩制之分。 <br />\n<br />\n港區人大代表、立法會議員田北辰則指，「結束一黨專政」口號屬於「踩界」行為，目前難以評論高叫有關口號人士會否被取消參選資格，他呼籲港人「少講為妙」。 <br />\n<br />\n身兼支聯會常委的街工立法會議員梁耀忠出席電台節目時稱，如果日後不可再講「結束一黨專政」口號，將打擊香港一國兩制及高度自治，並收窄言論空間，促請港府澄清「結束一黨專政」口號是否違法。"},{"pid":"6828b5dd45c8e20df229601d486a151915aa4d67","tid":599281,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c05010e85408afe8f51b5ee47eb306c8c048f36","tid":599281,"uid":57513,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:19:01.000Z","msg":"都玩帝制重學咩野人講憲法丫?<br />\non9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c6c9c23c008f8771dfc252cac7737c533fc6ad","tid":599281,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:23:25.000Z","msg":"建設帝制中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573130ab19206fef17515f3cd0b6beba77b24211","tid":599281,"uid":59901,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:23:33.000Z","msg":"呢個主任可以打靶，中華人民共和國嘅人大會議係包含共產黨以及其他的民主黨派，係偉大嘅制度，絕對也從來沒有一黨專政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1976eb2a195b59490437224ff0f98d0cd29bb208","tid":599281,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1e288219755abb563476dce0a4e3ee54ad9cd5e","tid":599281,"uid":47359,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:25:07.000Z","msg":"ok成個泛民收得皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw澳門中聯辦係咪五毛JR優美開始岩瀨健三啊頭?"},{"pid":"de7e46dc50ec110e46799146cdbe8f38e80b917c","tid":599281,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1976eb2a195b59490437224ff0f98d0cd29bb208","tid":599281,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6828b5dd45c8e20df229601d486a151915aa4d67","tid":599281,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:25:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛人見人愛<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/172536_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F172536_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=bf